[{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2018-02-22-software-craftsmanship-manifesto","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Fw: 軟體工藝宣言","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以下為〈軟體工藝宣言〉（Software Craftsmanship Manifesto）"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":"footnote-label","dataFootnoteRef":true,"id":"user-content-fnref-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":" 的複本。下列中文取自官方頁面的簡體中文版本，並且將詞彙轉為台灣社群慣用語以及〈敏捷軟體開發宣言〉的對應詞。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h5","props":{"id":"軟體工藝宣言"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"軟體工藝宣言"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"作為有理想的軟體工匠，我們一直身體力行，提升專業軟體開發的標準，並幫助他人學習此工藝。通過這些工作，我們建立了如下價值觀："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不僅要讓軟體可用，更要「精益求精」；"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n不僅要回應變化，更要「穩步增加價值」；"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n不僅要有個人與互動，更要「形成專業人員的社群」；"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n不僅要與客戶合作，更要「建立卓有成效的夥伴關係」。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"也就是說，左項固然值得追求，右項同樣不可或缺。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"原文如下："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h5","props":{"id":"software-craftsmanship-manifesto"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Software Craftsmanship Manifesto"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As aspiring Software Craftsmen we are raising the bar of professional software development by practicing it and helping others learn the craft. Through this work we have come to value:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Not only working software, but also well-crafted software"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNot only responding to change, but also steadily adding value"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNot only individuals and interactions, but also a community of professionals"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNot only customer collaboration, but also productive partnerships"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"That is, in pursuit of the items on the left we have found the items on the right to be indispensable."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"©2009，著作權為下述簽名者所有 "},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-2","ariaDescribedBy":"footnote-label","dataFootnoteRef":true,"id":"user-content-fnref-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n此宣言可以任何形式自由地複製，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n但其全文必須包含上述申明在內。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":true},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"className":["sr-only"],"id":"footnote-label"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Footnotes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Robert C Martin, and the undersigned (2009). Software Craftsmanship Manifesto. Retrieved from "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://manifesto.softwarecraftsmanship.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"http://manifesto.softwarecraftsmanship.org"}]},{"type":"text","value":"  "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1","ariaLabel":"Back to content","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"指有在官網簽署宣言的所有人 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-2","ariaLabel":"Back to content","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]}]}]}]},"title_en":"Software Craftsmanship Manifesto","slug":"software-craftsmanship-manifesto","aliases":["Fw: 軟體工藝宣言","Software Craftsmanship Manifesto"],"created_at":"2018-02-22T13:20:57.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":["foward"],"moc":["Agile"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2018-02-22-software-craftsmanship-manifesto.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2018-02-22-software-craftsmanship-manifesto.md","_extension":"md"},{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2018-04-05-aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"世紀帝國 II 系列：將中文介面下預設房間名稱改回英文","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我寫了第二個模組並發佈到 Steam 工作坊了！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1352725205","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Steam 工作坊 :: English Room Name in Chinese UI"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我想多數台灣玩家在玩 AoE II:HD 時，都會訂閱由 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steamcommunity.com/id/ZoeyHsieh","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Zoey Meow"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 製作的繁體中文化模組 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=466768643","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TChinese Zoey’s Work"}]},{"type":"text","value":"吧（嗯？這句好眼熟）。然而目前 AoE2:HD 尚未完整支援中文，尤其是在多人連線進度的儲存上，仍會時常遇到問題：倘若房間名稱包含中文時，會導致無法儲存遊戲，並且跳出類似於下面的訊息："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"寫入多人連線存擋遊戲時發生錯誤！你的磁碟空間可能已經用完。無法打開文件: C\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\Age2HD\\savegame\\multi\\Ruoshi的房間-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx.aoe2mpgame"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"或是如下圖："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"![AoE2HD-English-Room-Name-mod 1.png](AoE2HD-English-Room-Name-mod 1.png)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以每次和朋友打團時，總要不免其煩的更改房間名稱，改久了也是會發懶的。於是朋友就提到，我既然已經會建立模組了，何不順便寫一個模組，讓房間名稱是英文的呢？這一聽之下覺得可行，就動手做了，馬上將願望成真！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"畢竟這是遊戲本身的問題，你要中文化模組作者再把房間名稱從「<玩家>的房間」改回「<玩家>’s game」也說不過去。這時候若有一個小模組能讓我們享受中文化模組的同時，也能不用再改房間名稱，等日後官方解決這個缺陷，再將這個小模組停用，這豈不是皆大歡喜。XD"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"於是本模組就誕生啦！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前 AoE2:HD 尚未完整支援中文，尤其是在多人連線進度的儲存上，仍會時常遇到問題，導致遇到狀況無法先儲存再另外打過。但是每次開房都要更改房間名稱，又實在是一件很繁瑣且容易忘記的事情。本模組則是幫助使用中文語系的玩家們，在開房時房名仍維持英文語系的預設值，不再需要另外改名稱、或是因為忘記改名稱而懊悔啦！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"簡單來說，就是讓本模組將被中文化模組翻譯過的房名從「<玩家>的房間」再改回英文版預設的「<玩家>’s game」，讓我們不用在因為忘記改房名導致無法存檔囉！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若好奇這個模組是怎麼運作的，本模組的相關程式碼與資源也放在 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/fntsrlike/AoE2-English-Room-Name","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GitHub – fntsrlike/AoE2-English-Room-Name"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 上了，有興趣的朋友可以前往參考。"}]}]},"title_en":"AoE II: [Mod] English Room Name in Chinese UI","slug":"aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui","aliases":["世紀帝國 II 系列：將中文介面下預設房間名稱改回英文","AoE II: [Mod] English Room Name in Chinese UI"],"created_at":"2018-04-05T17:41:20.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":["aoe","translation"],"moc":["Games"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2018-04-05-aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2018-04-05-aoe-ii-mod-english-room-name-in-chinese-ui.md","_extension":"md"}]